    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's the perfect fit for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. It runs super smoothly and is totally ready for its next big adventure! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
