    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a dependable, well-maintained example that performs excellently on the road. The engine is responsive and the transmission shifts seamlessly, reflecting a consistent service history. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows only light wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all interior electronics\u2014from the navigation system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014are fully operational. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the trunk lid. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes were recently serviced. This is a solid, turnkey car that offers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and sophisticated design. This unit features a robust powertrain and a well-preserved interior, ensuring a premium driving experience. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, it stands as a testament to diligent ownership. We invite serious inquiries to experience the exceptional value and performance this motorcar offers.",
