    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "For sale is a driver-focused example featuring a high-revving naturally aspirated flat-six mated to a precise short-throw 6-speed manual transmission. This chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity and is equipped with an active suspension management system (PASM) and a mechanical limited-slip differential for superior turn-in and corner exit traction. Recent service includes a comprehensive borescope inspection, oil analysis, and a refresh of the cooling system components. The mid-engine layout provides neutral handling dynamics, while the upgraded four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors ensure consistent thermal management under load. Minor cosmetic road rash consistent with spirited use, but mechanically sound with a documented service history.",
